en_3162368_0	The public opinion poll for the constitutional reforms commenced in the Kandy and Gampaha Districts on Monday, February 1.
en_3162368_1	Chairman of the Public Representations Committee on Constitutional Reforms, Lal Wijenayake said that the poll will be conducted on Monday and Tuesday at the Kandy and Gampaha district secretariats.
en_3162368_2	He stated that votes can be cast in the opinion poll via phone calls, fax, e-mail and postal services.
